@startuml

title Sequence Diagram for Map Creation

actor Editor
participant "CreateMapUI" as UI
participant "CreateMapController" as Controller
participant "MapService" as Service
participant "MapRepository" as Repository

Editor -> UI: Open map creation interface
UI -> Editor: Request map name, width, height
Editor -> UI: Input map name, width, height
UI -> Controller: Submit map creation request
Controller -> Service: Validate map name
Service -> Repository: Check name uniqueness
Repository -> Service: Return uniqueness result
Service -> Controller: Validate map size
Controller -> Service: Create map
Service -> Repository: Save map
Repository -> Service: Confirm save
Service -> Controller: Return success message
Controller -> UI: Display success message
UI -> Editor: Show map creation success

@enduml
